msgid ""
"It is possible that the \"t-call\" time does not correspond to the overall "
"time of the\n"
"            template. Because the global time (in the drop down) does not "
"take into account the\n"
"            duration which is not in the rendering (look for the template, "
"read, inheritance,\n"
"            compilation...). During rendering, the global time also takes "
"part of the time to make\n"
"            the profile as well as some part not logged in the function "
"generated by the qweb."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je da vrijeme \"t-call\" ne odgovara ukupnom vremenu\n"
" predložaka. Zato što globalno vrijeme (u padajućem meniu) ne uzima u obzir\n"
" trajanje koje nije u renderiranju (potražite predložak, čitanje, "
"nasljeđivanje,\n"
" kompilaciju...). Tokom renderiranja, globalnom vremenu također treba dio "
"vremena da se napravi\n"
" profil, kao i dio koji nije prijavljen u funkciju koju generiše qweb."

